<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css"
    integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg=="
    crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/ck.css">    


    <title>CPUCARE-Software Installation  and Remote Support Service</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
    <%- include("../includes/header.ejs")%>
    <main class="flex justify-between gap-x-14 px-14 py-4 mt-8">
        <section class="w-1/2">
            <div class=" h-96 px-8 py-4 bg-white rounded-lg flex flex-col  items-center gap-y-4">
                <img src="/update_2.png" alt="" class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-orange-400">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-house-laptop text-4xl text-yellow-400"></i>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-500">Software Installation + <span class="text-yellow-500">Remote Support</span></h3>
                <p>Installing new software is like giving your device a fresh upgrade. It can streamline tasks, boost performance, and open up new possibilities.With the power of remote support, technical assistance is always within reach, making it easier than ever to keep your devices running smoothly.</p>
            </div>

        </section>
        <section class="w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-y-4">
            <h5 class="font-bold text-xl">Price: 160$</h5>
            <form action="/customer" class="flex flex-col gap-y-6" method="post">
                <input type="text" class="px-2 py-2 border border-black rounded-md" name="username" id="" placeholder="Your Name (required)" required>
                <input type="email" class="px-2 py-2 border border-black rounded-md" name="email" id="" placeholder="Your Email (required)" required>
                <input type="text" class="px-2 py-2 border border-black rounded-md" name="Phone" id="" placeholder="Your Phone Number (required)" required>
                <textarea name="message" id="" placeholder="YOUR MESSAGE" class="px-2 py-1 border-2 border-black rounded-md"
                required></textarea>

                <button class="px-2 py-3 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-md">Purchase</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include("../includes/footer.ejs")%>
</body>
</html>